        "content": "## 🧠 Foxtrot AI Chatbot (Agentic RAG)\n**Purpose:** A conversational Discord bot that can answer team questions and fetch personal ClickUp tasks on demand.\n**How it works:** When a user DMs the bot, the workflow looks up their specific ClickUp ID via Google Sheets. It then passes the message to a Gemini-powered Agent. The Agent acts as a normal chatbot unless the user asks about their tasks, in which case it autonomously triggers the ClickUp API tool, formats the tasks nicely, and replies in Discord.",
